jobAppEmail.emailText:
To those at {$cName},

	Congratulations, you just received a new job application! A Vize user, {$wName}, has responded to your job post (which was given id={$jId}). They provided the contact information below, feel free to contact them directly.

	If you have any issues with this process, please let us know. If you hire this employee, please send us a message letting us know what you think of our service. We hope you've found the perfect employee for your company and the position!

All the best,

	The Vize Team

